_sText:
This is a bundle pack of all the variants of my map kirgarage! (kir stands for keep it real)

Inside includes:

* de_kirgarage: Bombsite, with buyzones; normal play.

* gg_kirgarage: No bombsite, no buyzones; just a fightyard style of map for gun game.

* gg_de_kirgarage: Bombsite, no buyzones; bombsite oriented gun game map. 
                    (Some gun game mods have bombs/defusals as level ups)

Contact me for anything regarding source :|
